00:10:53.307 --> 00:10:54.765
Ejekan dipanggang di 'Ghee'.

00:10:55.349 --> 00:10:58.141
Dimarahi marah.

00:10:58.558 --> 00:11:01.057
Wow LUAR BIASA!

00:11:04.266 --> 00:11:07.516
Kamu peduli tentang Sai
tapi bukan tentang istrimu.

00:11:07.890 --> 00:11:11.558
Anda punya makanan untuk Sai.

00:11:11.890 --> 00:11:15.682
